A simple animation sketch for the Peggy2, made for Halloween 2009 by Jeremy Seitz. 

Requires:
- Peggy2: http://evilmadscience.com/tinykitlist/75
- Peggy2 library: http://code.google.com/p/peggy/
- Metro lib: http://www.arduino.cc/playground/Code/Metro

I used BMP2peg to convert my own images.
http://code.google.com/p/peggy/downloads/detail?name=bmp2peg_1.0.zip


Compile and upload to your Peggy2. 

